cast.overview: When an IMF mission ends badly, the world is faced with dire consequences. As Ethan Hunt takes it upon himself to fulfill his original briefing, the CIA begin to question his loyalty and his motives. The IMF team find themselves in a race against time, hunted by assassins while trying to prevent a global catastrophe.
cast.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout

details.biography: Godiva Marshall is an Actress, Dancer, Choreographer and Teacher known for The Outlaws (2021), EastEnders (1985) and The Duchess (2020). Training: Identity School of Acting, Actors Temple; Rambert School of Ballet & Contemporary Dance. Phoenix Dance Theatre. Godiva holds a Masters of Teaching at the Royal Academy of Dance. She has taught extensively from novice to professional level dancers both nationally and internationally including performing at the Cultural Olympiad Atlanta with Phoenix Dance Theatre. She is a dynamic artist and educator, and an original cast member of The Lion King production.
details.name: Godiva Marshall
